{
  "texts": [
    "Several works focus on designing specialized strategies to enhance agent capabilities.",
    "Guan et al. (2024) introduces AMOR, an agent framework that constructs its reasoning capabilities on a Finite State Machine (FSM).",
    "Li et al. (2024c) introduce a \"Formal-LLM\" framework for agents, combining the expressiveness of natural language with the precision of formal language to enhance agent capabilities.",
    "Research efforts (Jiang et al., 2023b; Dou et al., 2024; Yang et al., 2024b) have also explored self-improvement approaches, where models continuously enhance their problem-solving abilities through iterative learning in complex tasks.",
    "Knowledge-Augmented LLMs."
  ]
}